How to install the binary :
---------------------------
If you are using 32-bit machine - run
sudo cp bin/32-bit/* /usr/bin
If you are using 64-bit machine - run
sudo cp bin/64-bit/* /usr/bin
then execute with the command:
words

How to install binary from source:
---------------------------------
Under GNU/Linux, compile it:
g++ words.cpp -o copy/words 
and copy the files:
sudo cp copy/* /usr/bin
then execute with the command:
words
